  "texts": [
    "These databases are designed to facilitate the system's comprehension of the user's queries and to enable speedy retrieval.",
    "In order to deliver context-aware responses to user queries, the AI Study Partner first looks up the user's chat history in the SQL database.",
    "The system use a Retriever, like the Open AI Service Text Embedding Model, to locate the most pertinent search embeddings that align with the query's purpose when the inquiry is new or requires additional information.After the data is obtained, it is sent into a Response Generator, which uses GPT models.",
    "Flow Chart -3: Document SummarizationLarge Language Models (LLMs) are utilized in the summarization feature for both small and large documents, taking a divide-and-conquer strategy for processing effectiveness.",
    "Document into smaller, easier-to-manage sections."
  ]
}